    <section id="about">
        <div class="container mb-5">
            <div class="heading">
                <h2>About <span>Us</span></h2>
            </div>
            <h3>Your Dream Wedding Begins Here</h3>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-sm-12 me-2 mt-3">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/about.jpeg" alt="Wedding Image">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-sm-12 me-2 mt-3">
                    <p>
                        Welcome to our specialized wedding services website! We are dedicated to making your special
                        day truly memorable by offering a comprehensive range of services tailored to meet all your
                        wedding planning needs.
                        <br><br>
                        Our website is designed to provide you with everything you need for a perfect wedding
