                You can use the following contact information if you encounter any issues or have
                any inquiries about our services. Your feedback and requests are also welcome ,  feel free to reach out to us
                either by direct call or by filling out the form below.
            </p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-5 col-5 col-sm-12 me-2 mt-3">
                    <div class="contact-box">
                        <h3 style="color: #3c734c;" class="mb-4">Main Office</h3>
                        <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Example Street, New York, USA</p>
                        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 123 456 7890</p>
                        <p><strong>Email:</strong> support@example.com</p>
                        <p><strong>WhatsApp:</strong> +1 987 654 3210</p>
                        <p><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 9 AM - 5 PM</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-5 col-sm-12 me-2 mt-3">
                    <h3 style="color: #3c734c;">Send a Message</h3>
                    <form>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter your name">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter your email">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label">Message</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="Write your message here"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn w-100 bg-success bg-opacity-75">Send</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
